beer.beer_description: This bright pale ale bucks the trend of mega quantities of peach and passionfruit. Instead, the Strata and Amarillo aroma hops impart subtle notes that, if in a wine, might be expressed as barnyard. The dry finish results in a crisp, refreshing beer that is perfect for every summer day - not just 11 of them!
